  "keyFeatures": [
    "Centralized Layer 4 and Layer 7 load balancing",
    "Multi-cluster management with hub-and-spoke architecture",
    "Envoy-based traffic routing with xDS control plane",
    "Support for Services, Ingress, and Gateway API",
    "Multi-tenant isolation and security",
    "Flexible Envoy proxy deployment topologies",
    "DNS and TLS certificate automation",
    "Prometheus metrics and monitoring"
